# Design an update

A user has asked to update an existing skill. Read the skill
on disk, then produce a structured change plan that the user
can review and approve before any files are touched.

## Inputs

- `gather-update` output:
  `{{ upstream['gather-update'].task_path }}`
  Carries `name`, `namespace`, `path`, `type`, `skill_dir`,
  `category`, `description` (the user's change request).
- The skill on disk at `{{ vars.skill_dir }}` — `fs_read`
  SKILL.md and any `references/` or `scripts/` files needed
  to understand the change.

